<bibRefCitation author="QUATE L. &amp; BROWN B." box="[436,706,301,324]" pageId="12" pageNumber="469" pagination="1 - 117" refId="ref7299" refString="QUATE L. &amp; BROWN B. 2004: Revision of Neotropical Setomimini (Diptera: Psychodidae: Psychodinae). Contribution in Science: Natural History Museum of Los Angeles 500: 1 - 117." type="journal article" year="2004">QUATE &amp; BROWN (2004)</bibRefCitation>
